t": "真正的文人风骨是怎样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "风骨用来形容人，始自《晋书·赫连勃勃载记》的史臣论赞。原文如下： 「赫连勃勃獯丑种类，入居边宇，属中壤分崩，缘间肆慝，控弦鸣镝，据有朔方。遂乃法玄象以开宫，拟神京而建社，窃先王之徽号，备中国之礼容，驱驾英贤，窥窬天下。然其器识高爽，风骨魁奇，姚兴睹之而醉心，宋祖闻之而动色。岂阴山之韫异气，不然何以致斯乎！虽雄略过人，而凶残未革，饰非距谏，酷害朝臣，部内嚣然，忠良卷舌。灭亡之祸，宜在厥身，犹及其嗣，非不幸也。」 所以，形容一个人有风骨，需要有如下条件： 1. 獯丑种类 2. 窥窬天下 3. 阴山之韫异气，不然何以致斯 4. 凶残未革，饰非距谏， 5. 灭亡之祸，宜在厥身，犹及其嗣。 符合上述条件，不是一般的文人可以做到的。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-45114d1b5942554a14bfc80b72903e11_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/560396374"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9aDC8t6JlMZREAMaCDg2ODE1MzIyILKiuJoGMAA4vwJAIHIJNTYwMzk2Mzc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1718280992.759289", "card_id": "Q_440613841", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "陕西渭南市有着大片的平原地区，为什么发展不起来？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8dae26777219d362e16704c20e05ce4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/440613841"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9aDC8t6JlMZREAMaCDYwMTkyMTY1IMLOqYAGMAA4PUAhcgk0NDA2MTM4NDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1718280992.759478", "card_id": "Q_657535086", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "不需要上班的生活就一定会自由舒适吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d4fef1c0a965d4e6c060362533a76185_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"